                <li>Unity software development for exhibitions and museums</li>
                <li>AI camera integration for face and body detection</li>
                <li>NAS data migration and temporary administration</li>
                <li>CI/CD build automation with cloud services</li>
                <li>Internal Unity tools for designers (balancers, content pooling generators)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-card">
              <h3>IT Technician</h3>
              <span class="experience-meta">Institut de l’Arboç · Sept 2020 – May 2021</span>
              <ul>
                <li>Hardware repair and device installation</li>
                <li>Windows and Linux OS installation</li>
                <li>Server administration and maintenance</li>
