              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- EDUCATION -->
          <section class="experience-section">
            <h2>Education</h2>

            <div class="experience-card">
              <h3>Higher Degree in Multimedia Applications & Video Games</h3>
              <span class="experience-meta">Institut Pedralbes · 2019 – 2021</span>
              <p>2D, 3D and VR Development · Unity · Unreal Engine</p>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-card">
              <h3>CISCO CCNA 1 Certification</h3>
              <span class="experience-meta">Eugeni D'Ors · 2020</span>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-card">
              <h3>Vocational Training – Microcomputer Systems and Networks</h3>
              <span class="experience-meta">Eugeni d'Ors · 2018 – 2020</span>
              <p>Network Configuration · Hardware Maintenance · Operating Systems</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- HIGHLIGHTED PROJECTS -->
          <section class="experience-section">
            <h2>Highlighted Projects</h2>

            <div class="experience-card">
              <h3><a class="experience-link" href="/personal-projects#:~:text=Unf0und_VR%20%2D%20Horror%20VR%20Experience">Unf0und VR</a></h3>
              <p>VR paranormal experience developed in Unity using C#.</p>
              <span class="experience-meta">Finalist – 14th FPemprèn edition</span>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-card">
              <h3><a class="experience-link" href="/personal-projects#:~:text=Demo%20Playable%20Horror%20Game">Demo Playable Horror Game</a></h3>
              <p>FP Horror Game · Character creation</p>
            </div>

            <div class="experience-card">
              <h3><a class="experience-link" href="/personal-projects#:~:text=Demo%20Slot%20Machine">Demo Slot Machine</a></h3>
              <p>Modular betting application · Fully customizable and adjustable</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <!-- PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY -->
          <section class="experience-section">
            <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
            <p class="experience-card">
              I am a Video Game and Software Developer focused on Unity, Unreal Engine, and C++ development.
              I have experience building interactive experiences, internal developer tools, and scalable game systems.
              I value clean architecture, performance optimization, and adaptable workflows.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
